Note on write-ups
-----------------
The strain write-ups in data/writeups/ are AI-generated, unverified drafts.
They are provided as a starting point only. Corrections and verified additions
are welcome via the project's contribution process.

Third-party map data
--------------------
The world map geometry in data/world.geojson is NOT part of the CC BY-SA dataset
above. It is derived from Natural Earth (https://www.naturalearthdata.com/),
whose vector map data is released into the public domain. "Made with Natural Earth."

Map rendering uses the Leaflet library (data/../lib/leaflet/, BSD-2-Clause) and the
marked Markdown renderer (lib/marked.min.js, MIT); each retains its own upstream
license.
